A page from the technical specification of deployed drones
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copter


Copters are our most flexible units. They are fast and can fly over water.
That makes them a perfect choice for guarding naval areas. 
A copter's detection radius is extremely high and its height allows a big 'sight' angle. 


Armor type: Light

Weapon type: Machine gun

Damage: 3

Chaussie type: Flying (Can cross almost every terrain)

Max Life: 20

Speed factor: 3


Weaknesses: 


Copters don't have good armor and can be shot down fast with rapid-fire weapons, such as assault rifles.   


 

 



  